001package imagingbook.calibration.data.zhang;
002
003import imagingbook.core.resource.NamedResource;
004
005public enum TextDataResource implements NamedResource {
006                CalibrationResultZhangWithDistortion_txt("Calibration-result-zhang-withdistortion.txt"),
007                Model_txt("Model.txt"),
008                AllCalibrationResultsEasyCalib_txt("all-calibration-results-EasyCalib.txt"),
009                AllCalibrationResults_txt("all-calibration-results.txt"),
010                Data1_txt("data1.txt"),
011                Data2_txt("data2.txt"),
012                Data3_txt("data3.txt"),
013                Data4_txt("data4.txt"),
014                Data5_txt("data5.txt");
015
016        private final static String BASEDIR = "DATA";
017        private final String filename;
018        
019        private TextDataResource(String filename) {
020                this.filename = filename;
021        }
022
023        @Override
024        public String getFileName() {
025                return filename;
026        }
027        
028        @Override
029        public String getRelativeDirectory() {
030                return BASEDIR;
031        }
032        
033        public static void main(String[] args) {
034                for (NamedResource nr : TextDataResource.values()) {
035                        System.out.println(nr.getURL());
036                }
037        }
038
039}
